Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.09,0:00:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When watching Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep the room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Sora Naegino.\NI came to America all by myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with aspirations of joining Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything is new to me, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I'm doing my best in the spirit\Nof "try it rather than think about it."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing I can't do if I try,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and if I can do it without\Ntrying, that'll be super lucky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I'm gonna do it, I just\Ngotta do it! Gotta! Gotta! That's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well, everyone,\Ndo you have a pet at home?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A pet that you feed and take on walks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can be quite troublesome. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But still, they're adorable, aren't they?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, they're a member of the family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how much he's against it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:01:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not gonna give up this time\Neither! Not gonna! Not gonna!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yaritai koto wa nani {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sou kikareru tabi {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aoi sora miageta {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kotae wa only my heart {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Honto ni daiji na kotoba\Nwa kantan ni wa iwanai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hikari ga yubisasu\Nbasho e to hashiridasu yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dakishimetai mono nara\Nnakitai hodo mune ni aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:02:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egakitsuzukete yuku kitto take it someday{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shiroi kumo ga nagareru\Nchiheisen no mukou ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naranderu mirai wa itsumo soba ni aru kara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage's Cinderella is a must-see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the show, the performance\Nof a trio of newcomers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the fairy godmothers was\Nfascinating during the climactic scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be watching these \Ngirls in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, watch us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The paper's praising us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:02:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it! We did it!\NWe did it! We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... a baby seal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Amazing Seal."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have gotten\Nseparated from his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be gone for just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of him, Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Take care of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall try reading your fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The upright Hanged Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card represents ordeals or sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may bring misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, can you see me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are wrong if you think \Nyou can be a Kaleido Star
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just because you can see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she left for\Nthe dining hall already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A misfortune is befalling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're praising the fairy godmothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have no eye for talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, if I were doing it,\Nthey would've praised us more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you'll hurt her \Nfeelings if she hears you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that would be like, awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right here. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering what he would like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I met him this morning\Nwhen I was jogging on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's cute, round, chubby,\Nsmall, and he's very hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What type of guy do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about any guy. He's a seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Se... Seal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't tell me you brought him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was hungry and I felt sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm not allowed to keep him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, he's still small, and\Nhe's probably just a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was weak, and he looked\Nlike he could die at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted to do something for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seals eat fresh fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to return him to the\Nsea once he recovers, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this! He's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, it is I who am in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he went back to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Who's Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This little guy was\Nscooting down the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was dragging this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he adorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way for me to keep him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just promise to\Nlet him go after feeding him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Jonathan could be\Na mascot for Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got lessons to go to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please look\Nafter him for a little while?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She does everything in her own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's what's so\Ngreat about her, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:07:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you read it? Did you read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did! I did! I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there! Quiet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a message from Kalos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the paper praised your performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Triple Illusion is far from perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not get carried away and lose your focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't he say that to us himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Kalos will \Nbe in Seattle for a week
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to attend a meeting about a new production.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new production?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be the meeting for\Nthe next production after Cinderella.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big projects like these\Ntake time to prepare for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, we'll be fine as\Nlong as we don't make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's practice hard for our Triple Illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, just you watch, Kalos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you burst out laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I found him at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for scaring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he was hungry\Nand I felt sorry for him, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can barely perform your own duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way you\Ncan look after an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him back right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took my eyes off him for just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked some veteran staff members,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they said that Kaleido Stage\Nhas never had any animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That seems to be Kalos's policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a good thing this\Nhappened while Kalos was away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't keep him, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's still just a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:10:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he can survive by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's small, but he'll \Neat quite a lot of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cost of feeding him won't be cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting a performer's pay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to start\Na part-time job tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part-time job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have lessons during the day\Nand performances in the evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, now is the most important time for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After my parents died, I was all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If no one had opened their arms to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I wouldn't be here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can't abandon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me a hypocrite,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I just can't abandon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work harder than ever on my performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for letting me use your bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome. But are you really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like it, Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to keep you \Nin such a cramped place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The inside of the drawer is also cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I have time off, let's go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach! Wearing bathing suits\Nis a great way to breed intimacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the two of us, Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She treats me worse than animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That is all for today's lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your Pirate Pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two orders of the Chef's Special,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linguine Bolognese.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The main entrees are sea bass and lobster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Signorina, here's today's pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But are you really sure you want\Nfresh fish instead of money every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he eats a lot of \Nfish, so this will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must really love fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still want more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't our timing for the\Ncross jump just perfect today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wish Kalos could have seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos just had to be gone \Nwhen we did it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Sora, are you going\Nto work after this again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been working\Nnon-stop for a whole week, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't push yourself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke one again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break another one and you're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have the day off tomorrow,\Nno performance or lessons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just hang in there a little longer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just missed dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I ran out of energy and I got dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not "dizzy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's why I told you not to push yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were working this many jobs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Jonathan eats so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he gets hungry really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this has to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't give up even if we try to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we have no choice but to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it can be done if we take turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:15:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is Jonathan's and my problem, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our problem too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just remembered something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juggling contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an annual event held on\Nthe outdoor stage at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the jugglers who are confident\Nin their skill participate in the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The contest is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,three days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who want to participate
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must register by 9 AM\Non the day of the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can anyone participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first prize could pay for a\Nwhole month of food for Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have no choice but to participate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you worried about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never juggled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could still be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we have three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup, yup, yup, yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The level of competition is high,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but as they say, "You've \Ngot nothing to lose."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.22,0:16:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start a crash course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The upright Wheel of Fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A messenger for good fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him? Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! I have great news!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you win the juggling contest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a month's worth of food for Jonathan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look. Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, so she already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Do it more rhythmically, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! If I can't even do something like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't expect to become a Kaleido Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you were that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there was a cast\Nmember who tried to keep a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and got fired by Kalos for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad said that Kalos\Nis coming back Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan, you're better than Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan, you're good! Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! You're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jonathan, do it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he won't\Ndo it unless he feels like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He acts just like a big star.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Jonathan can do it, I should be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's go for the crowd pleaser.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the juggling contest\Nis getting more exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up are regulars you already\Nknow, Mr. and Mrs. Pumpkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, they're veteran performers for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wow! They're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be difficult for Sora's team to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I got back a day early.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This costume is tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because it's a rental.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the timing to\Nbring out the balls, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once Mia and Anna finish juggling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:59.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well, next up are three \Nvery attractive sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Anna, that's a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:01.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--the Jonathan Sisters! Here they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, it's Sora's group.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need them to do their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She blew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shoot! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were saved by Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo, Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:19:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he supposed to come back tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow you to work part-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor can I allow pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your attention\Nfocused on performing onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not losing my focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, when you were\Naway, we did a perfect...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This discussion is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to abandon Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I abandon him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot abandon him,\Nthen you should quit Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, you have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you the discussion is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the show has\Nnothing to do with Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, get rid of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time for something\Nlike that, you should practice more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will work harder than ever for the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that all the papers will come to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Kaleido Stage exists
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to make people happy when they come see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But abandoning Jonathan\Nin exchange for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's something wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I can't say what exactly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still think there's\Nsomething wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan... Everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos, now I understand why\Nyou let Sora join Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my biggest mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we take care of the seal here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, Sora can quit her part-time jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there won't be any worries\Nabout how he'll affect her performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you handle this, Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's build a gigantic\Nswimming pool for Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, Kalos gave you permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this great, Jonathan?
