Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They don't appreciate my performance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.84,0:23:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because the audience isn't \Nsophisticated enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, a talented diabolo\Ngirl, Rosetta, has come.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amazing... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.59,0:23:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She is truly the world champion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she looks sad somehow. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The stage is supposed to make\Nthe audience happy with our smiles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.25,0:23:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I wanna see\NRosetta smile no matter what.{\i0}
